seq_st: First sequence (starting at 0) of messages/heartbeats in a session at interval
seq_end: Last sequence of messages/heartbeats in a session at interval

bl.value: Average buffer length in ms for given resolution
bl.end: milliseconds from time window start. This value is MIN(end-of-window, heartbeat-ts)

br.end: milliseconds from time window start. This value is MIN(end-of-window, heartbeat-ts)
